project: ''Once upon a time, in a world oppressed by a powerful system, three warriorsSuli4Q, Tech N9ne, and 2Gunn Kevirose up to fight back. Suli4Qs words sparked hope, Tech N9nes rhymes struck fear into their enemies, and 2Gunn Kevis fearless spirit inspired resistance. Alone, they had faced the systems grip, but together, they formed an unstoppable force. United by music, grit, and determination, they vowed to tear down the walls of control.''
